parameters:
Blacksmith Carlf: I can't help but feel grateful to all of
you who made it possible for the ore to be delivered!

Blacksmith Carlf: Thank you for coming. I want you to go to
the Sufiri Mine and collect ore.
Thief Nora: Y-Yes, understood! Leave it to me!

Blacksmith Carlf: This is the harsh reality of Valier, once
renowned in the empire, unable to deliver what was requested
satisfactorily...
Thief Nora: Y-Yes, um... I will definitely bring it back!
Blacksmith Carlf: Ah, I've asked for your help.
Blacksmith Carlf: Sorry, I've finished the request.
Blacksmith Carlf: Oh, you brought it!

Thief Nora: U-Um, it seems that the leader has fallen ill
and is running late.

Blacksmith Carlf: I wonder how much of it is true... I guess
it means I should give up on doing business here.

Blacksmith Carlf: Anyway, I'm glad you helped. Oh, by the
way, I need to give you your reward.
Thief Nora: T-Thank you very much!

Blacksmith Carufu: I wonder if the shipment from the mine
will arrive today...
